VI Cheat sheet

:set number/nonumber --> toggle line number

Ctrl+b --> "page up"
Ctrl+f ---> "page down"

w --> move forward 1 word
b --> move backward 1 word

0 --> beginning of line
^ --> first character of line (think regex)
$ --> last character of line (think regex)

gg --> 1st line of file
ngg --> nth line of file
:$ --> move to last line of file

x --> delete character under the cursor
d --> delete something. operation{motion} (eg d0)
2d3w --> [count]operation[count]{motion}

. --> repeat previous issued command

p --> paste after cursor from clipboard
y --> yank/copy
u --> undo
